events.text:
a bag of pistachios fell out
do 'shelled pistachios' still have shells?
or is 'shelled' being used as the verb 'to remove pistachio shells'
would that mean that 'unshelled pistachios' have shells despite the 'un' prefix giving a negative force to its adjective and derivative adverb
.....
these pistachios still have shells on them
